description: At Mantraah, we believe in serving fresh, vegetarian, organic Indian street food made with locally sourced ingredients. We embrace “FRESHNESS” as the central ingredient of all our creations.Want to eat gluten-free, vegetarian, vegan, no onion-no Garlic, or just don’t like certain kinds of food? No problem. Just tell us what you want and we can customize your order.No time to drive? No-worries, we deliver to your office or home. Our freshly prepared meals offer a convenient way to eat healthy, delicious food at home or on-the-go. No shopping, no cooking, no cleaning, no hassles; just heat, eat, and enjoy!
name: Mantraah
